snippet.title: Sym.BIOS: Torn Asunder Character Presentation
snippet.description:
We’re happy to announce that Sym.BIOS: Torn Asunder will be released on Friday 4th August 2023!
The game will be available on that date on Steam and Itch to purchase for the small price of $13.99 or the equivalent currency in your country. 
Wishlist so you don’t miss it!
We spent nearly 2 years making this game, and we’re very curious to see your reactions. To go along we’ve prepared a short video presentation of all the main characters.
Not long to go now, see you then!

#visualnovel #scifi #indiegamedev #gaming #characters #multipleendings #choicesmatter
